WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:07.370
<i>The war between the Imperial Army and the 
Hellhorde has raged on for many years...</i>

3
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:17.550
<i>In the midst of battle, the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion</i>

4
00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:20.460
<i>falls into the hands of the Hellhorde.</i>

5
00:00:21.170 --> 00:00:26.410
<i>The Hellhorde, seeking to extract 
Imperial secrets from the princess...</i>

6
00:00:27.230 --> 00:00:30.500
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

7
00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:38.020
<i>...mercilessly subjects her 
to torture day after day.</i>

8
00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:47.840
So that's Hellholm.

9
00:00:49.290 --> 00:00:51.230
I'm here to save you...

10
00:00:52.750 --> 00:00:53.850
Your Highness!

11
00:00:59.650 --> 00:01:00.910
A theme park?

12
00:01:01.160 --> 00:01:02.120
Yeah!

13
00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:04.300
We just found out we have tomorrow off.

14
00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:06.540
S-So we were thinking of going.

15
00:01:06.870 --> 00:01:09.630
Wanna tag along, P-Princess-chan?

16
00:01:09.630 --> 00:01:11.260
There's no way!

17
00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:12.910
I'm a prisoner here!

18
00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:15.980
You should see if the grand 
inquisitor will let you go!

19
00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:17.970
C'mon!

20
00:01:22.980 --> 00:01:25.150
Okay! I'll ask!

21
00:01:25.150 --> 00:01:26.690
Awesome!

22
00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:30.070
I shouldn't just assume she'll say no!

23
00:01:30.070 --> 00:01:31.220
That's right!

24
00:01:31.220 --> 00:01:34.540
I-I'm sure it'll be real fun with you there.

25
00:01:34.540 --> 00:01:35.310
You said it!

26
00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:37.900
<i>C'mon, it's not happening.</i>

27
00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.450
You cannot go.

28
00:01:39.450 --> 00:01:40.520
Well, duh.

29
00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:42.500
You heartless monster!

30
00:01:42.750 --> 00:01:45.450
Are you saying that as a 
prisoner subject to torture,

31
00:01:45.450 --> 00:01:47.880
I don't have the freedom 
to visit a theme park?!

32
00:01:47.880 --> 00:01:49.710
I'm shocked that you thought you did.

33
00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:53.910
That said, how does this sound?

34
00:01:55.150 --> 00:01:58.500
I shall consider it in exchange 
for an imperial secret.

35
00:01:58.780 --> 00:02:00.270
You dirty scoundrel!

36
00:02:00.270 --> 00:02:01.890
So this is your torture for today?!

37
00:02:02.570 --> 00:02:04.560
I bet there <i>is</i> no theme park trip.

38
00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:06.920
It was all a trick to 
make Her Highness talk!

39
00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:07.890
On the contrary.

40
00:02:08.460 --> 00:02:10.360
I would not stoop so low.

41
00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:14.770
I imagine they invited you with 
naught but pure intentions.

42
00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:17.400
Don't let her fool you, Your Highness!

43
00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.000
Right then, onto business...

44
00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:25.070
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

45
00:02:40.180 --> 00:02:47.520
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

46
00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:03.450
You've been silent for an 
hour and counting now.

47
00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:05.430
Are you sure about this?

48
00:04:05.430 --> 00:04:07.610
The park is almost about to open.

49
00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:12.660
If you confess, I can send you to the 
park with a teleportation spell.

50
00:04:13.530 --> 00:04:16.840
Don't you want to enjoy 
yourself with the others?

51
00:04:17.570 --> 00:04:18.870
Your Highness,

52
00:04:18.870 --> 00:04:21.490
Youki and Inki were simply 
acting on her orders.

53
00:04:21.490 --> 00:04:23.050
Their invite was nothing but a sham.

54
00:04:23.050 --> 00:04:24.560
Rest assured, Ex.

55
00:04:25.300 --> 00:04:29.420
I am Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

56
00:04:29.980 --> 00:04:32.530
I've seen my fair share of battles.

57
00:04:33.550 --> 00:04:35.290
There are times when those 
I considered comrades...

58
00:04:38.310 --> 00:04:40.360
ended up betraying me.

59
00:04:51.690 --> 00:04:54.040
This is nothing new to me.

60
00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:56.230
I won't give in, by any means.

61
00:05:00.220 --> 00:05:01.950
'Tis time for the park to open.

62
00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:06.610
I regret to say that you 
have bested me on this day.

63
00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:08.610
Y-Your Highness.

64
00:05:08.610 --> 00:05:10.480
Please don't let it get to you.

65
00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:11.690
I'm totally fine!

66
00:05:11.690 --> 00:05:13.870
I told you, I'm used to it!

67
00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:16.500
That said...

68
00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:19.090
We're friends, aren't we?

69
00:05:19.290 --> 00:05:22.770
I-I'm sure it'll be real fun with you there.

70
00:05:22.770 --> 00:05:23.580
You said it!

71
00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:29.070
I might have wanted to go on 
that trip a little bit...

72
00:05:29.580 --> 00:05:30.970
Your Highness...

73
00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:46.530
Youki

74
00:05:38.300 --> 00:05:41.320
<i>We'll be waiting outside until you get here!</i>

75
00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:46.530
We'll be waiting outside
until you get here~

76
00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:46.530
Inki

77
00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:46.530
We'll be waiting~

78
00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:43.080
<i>We'll be waiting!</i>

79
00:05:46.770 --> 00:05:49.780
Our friendship is the real deal!

80
00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:52.080
I'll tell you!

81
00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:54.290
I told you they weren't lying...

82
00:05:55.370 --> 00:05:58.120
The princess 
confessed

83
00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:00.950
Did Princess-chan reply yet?

84
00:06:09.010 --> 00:06:10.670
I'm here!

85
00:06:10.670 --> 00:06:12.050
Oh, there you are!

86
00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.800
Th-That outfit...

87
00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:15.330
You look super cute!

88
00:06:15.980 --> 00:06:17.510
Really?

89
00:06:17.510 --> 00:06:18.400
All right!

90
00:06:18.630 --> 00:06:20.870
Let's have ourselves a blast today!

91
00:06:20.870 --> 00:06:22.330
Yeah!

92
00:06:24.860 --> 00:06:26.240
<i>This is so fun!</i>

93
00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.570
<i>I'm so happy!</i>

94
00:06:27.570 --> 00:06:29.150
<i>What a brand-new experience!</i>

95
00:06:29.660 --> 00:06:31.610
<i>It's so nice to have friends!</i>

96
00:06:31.610 --> 00:06:38.000
<i>Having fun with others makes it two, 
three, four, five times as fun!</i>

97
00:06:39.390 --> 00:06:42.060
<i>My heart won't stop dancing with joy!</i>

98
00:06:49.190 --> 00:06:52.740
<i>Welcome to Tokyo...</i>

99
00:06:54.390 --> 00:06:55.340
Yes.

100
00:06:55.640 --> 00:07:00.220
It took until the very end, but we've 
finally obtained a useful piece of intelligence.

101
00:07:00.810 --> 00:07:04.370
Their king... prefers sea over land.

102
00:07:04.930 --> 00:07:08.270
Will the secret we've coaxed 
out of her today suffice?

103
00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:09.530
What?

104
00:07:10.230 --> 00:07:12.140
Oh, yes.

105
00:07:12.140 --> 00:07:13.360
The same as always.

106
00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:14.690
What?!

107
00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.800
Understood.

108
00:07:18.670 --> 00:07:20.270
Tomorrow's torture session...

109
00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.920
will be handled personally 
by His Majesty's daughter?

110
00:07:26.690 --> 00:07:30.420
Earthen cradle under heaven's watchful gaze.

111
00:07:30.830 --> 00:07:32.640
Hush-a-bye baby.

112
00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:36.420
March thee onward, to the city 
cloaked in night eternal.

113
00:07:36.430 --> 00:07:40.430
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

114
00:07:37.310 --> 00:07:38.590
Besties for life!

115
00:07:48.710 --> 00:07:51.040
Why are you kneeling?

116
00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:52.920
Oh, is it me?

117
00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.790
Have you realized how great I am?

118
00:07:54.790 --> 00:07:56.370
I'm pretty sure it's not that.

119
00:07:56.680 --> 00:08:01.440
I kneel not in deference to you, Princess.

120
00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:05.120
Today's torture will be performed 
by His Majesty's daughter.

121
00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:07.080
The daughter of the Hell-Lord?!

122
00:08:07.650 --> 00:08:08.710
Indeed.

123
00:08:09.210 --> 00:08:11.420
The only daughter of His 
Majesty the Hell-Lord.

124
00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:15.590
Hyper Cadet Harm-Marshal...

125
00:08:17.390 --> 00:08:19.850
Hell-Lord's Daughter
Hyper Cadet Harm-Marshal
    Maomao-chan

126
00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:19.860
Her Highness Princess Maomao-chan.

127
00:08:19.860 --> 00:08:21.880
So cute!

128
00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:24.080
Oh, what a cutie pie!

129
00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:25.620
So small!

130
00:08:25.620 --> 00:08:27.280
How old are you, Maomao-chan?

131
00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:28.580
Go on, go on!

132
00:08:28.580 --> 00:08:31.030
Ask me whatever you want!

133
00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:31.600
Your Highness?

134
00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:34.420
I-It's not what you think, Ex.

135
00:08:34.420 --> 00:08:39.070
I was just trying to get some information 
out of the Hell-Lord's daughter.

136
00:08:39.070 --> 00:08:40.570
Look me in the eye and say that.

137
00:08:41.090 --> 00:08:43.550
She's the daughter of none 
other than the Hell-Lord.

138
00:08:43.550 --> 00:08:45.620
Don't let her age catch you off guard!

139
00:08:45.620 --> 00:08:46.950
Nuh-uh.

140
00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:51.330
I'm no good at all.

141
00:08:52.330 --> 00:08:55.170
Everyone has big hopes for 
me because of my dad...

142
00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:59.350
but I've never gotten anything 
out of anyone with torture.

143
00:09:02.980 --> 00:09:08.590
I... must not be cut out to be a torturer...

144
00:09:11.180 --> 00:09:12.700
That's not true!

145
00:09:12.700 --> 00:09:14.940
That's not true at all, Maomao-chan!

146
00:09:15.190 --> 00:09:17.330
Even if it seems like nothing 
ever goes your way,

147
00:09:17.330 --> 00:09:20.610
I promise your efforts will pay off one day!

148
00:09:20.830 --> 00:09:23.210
Your Highness, why are you 
encouraging the enemy?

149
00:09:23.510 --> 00:09:27.290
So be a brave girl now, and torture me!

150
00:09:28.970 --> 00:09:30.970
Thanks, missy!

151
00:09:31.340 --> 00:09:32.940
Oh, you're adorable! I'll talk!

152
00:09:32.940 --> 00:09:34.410
Don't jump the gun, Your Highness!

153
00:09:34.410 --> 00:09:35.610
Okay!

154
00:09:35.610 --> 00:09:36.720
Well then...

155
00:09:37.030 --> 00:09:39.880
It's time for torture, Princess!

156
00:09:42.030 --> 00:09:44.970
Um, this is bubble wrap.

157
00:09:44.970 --> 00:09:48.870
I love popping the bubbles.

158
00:09:48.870 --> 00:09:52.630
So popping them in front of 
you should make you jealous!

159
00:09:53.230 --> 00:09:53.690
<i>Pop</i>

160
00:09:53.980 --> 00:09:54.490
<i>Pop</i>

161
00:09:54.740 --> 00:09:55.190
<i>Pop</i>

162
00:09:56.990 --> 00:09:57.490
<i>Pop</i>

163
00:09:57.740 --> 00:09:58.200
<i>Pop</i>

164
00:09:58.490 --> 00:09:58.910
<i>Pop</i>

165
00:09:59.240 --> 00:09:59.660
<i>Pop</i>

166
00:10:02.170 --> 00:10:04.500
Well? Aren't you <i>so</i> jealous?!

167
00:10:06.330 --> 00:10:08.050
<i>God, she's cute.</i>

168
00:10:08.050 --> 00:10:10.340
<i>To be honest, I don't feel jealous at all.</i>

169
00:10:10.340 --> 00:10:13.030
<i>And yet, I want to tell 
her a secret so badly!</i>

170
00:10:13.030 --> 00:10:14.510
Keep it together, Your Highness!

171
00:10:14.900 --> 00:10:17.970
Princess Maomao-chan, you're almost there.

172
00:10:19.770 --> 00:10:22.380
How about this, then?

173
00:10:22.650 --> 00:10:25.730
My awesome move where you 
pop a whole bunch at once!

174
00:10:32.690 --> 00:10:36.730
This bold move uses up a 
ton of bubbles in no time,

175
00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:39.860
so I only use it on very special days!

176
00:10:40.310 --> 00:10:43.650
<i>This is killing me more than 
any of the previous tortures!</i>

177
00:10:43.650 --> 00:10:44.830
Hang in there, Your Highness!

178
00:10:44.830 --> 00:10:46.070
Get a hold of yourself!

179
00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:48.720
Okay, just a little more!

180
00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:50.650
Um, next is...

181
00:10:53.210 --> 00:10:57.630
I'm all out of bubbles to pop...

182
00:10:58.950 --> 00:11:02.080
I messed up at torturing again...

183
00:11:02.610 --> 00:11:04.780
After I tried so hard, too...

184
00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:08.900
I'll tell you everything!

185
00:11:09.140 --> 00:11:12.150
The princess 
confessed

186
00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:14.280
I see.

187
00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:17.480
So this is the Imperial Army's secret code.

188
00:11:17.830 --> 00:11:19.860
Am I done with all my work now?

189
00:11:19.860 --> 00:11:21.360
Yes, that's right.

190
00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:24.250
'Twas perfect, Princess Maomao-chan.

191
00:11:24.250 --> 00:11:28.210
And now that she's divulged her secret, 
we're done with the princess.

192
00:11:28.710 --> 00:11:31.260
Feel free to do as you wish with her.

193
00:11:32.040 --> 00:11:35.060
Um, then...

194
00:11:38.610 --> 00:11:40.500
Let's play a game of tag!

195
00:11:42.020 --> 00:11:43.270
Sure!

196
00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:48.370
Maomao-chan!

197
00:11:48.370 --> 00:11:50.060
Look, I'm right here!

198
00:11:51.430 --> 00:11:53.680
Wait for me!

199
00:11:54.210 --> 00:11:56.840
C'mon, catch me if you can!

200
00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:57.840
Okay!

201
00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:59.700
I'll get you!

202
00:12:00.470 --> 00:12:03.980
Your Highness, did you 
just undo your chains?

203
00:12:00.690 --> 00:12:02.250
Over here!

204
00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:03.980
Wait up, missy!

205
00:12:03.980 --> 00:12:05.260
Tag!

206
00:12:05.260 --> 00:12:07.420
Ah, you got me!

207
00:12:07.420 --> 00:12:09.380
Now <i>you're</i> it!

208
00:12:11.220 --> 00:12:12.490
Well, well.

209
00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:16.000
Play nice
Aim to learn
Live
positively

210
00:12:12.980 --> 00:12:15.450
So this is their secret code.

211
00:12:15.450 --> 00:12:16.000
Yes, sir.

212
00:12:16.650 --> 00:12:20.170
Let us make haste and deliver that 
note to the Chief Officer of Combat.

213
00:12:20.170 --> 00:12:21.160
Not a chance!

214
00:12:22.030 --> 00:12:25.620
This is Maomao-chan's first 
accomplishment at work!

215
00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:28.570
I'm going to frame it and hang it in my home.

216
00:12:29.530 --> 00:12:31.900
I won't let anyone else see it!

217
00:12:32.140 --> 00:12:34.400
Play nice
Aim to learn
Live
positively

218
00:12:34.900 --> 00:12:37.990
March thee onward, to the city 
cloaked in night eternal.

219
00:12:38.700 --> 00:12:41.730
Head yonder to dreams impossible.

220
00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:46.250
Earthen cradle under heaven's watchful gaze.

221
00:12:49.160 --> 00:12:52.000
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

222
00:12:54.220 --> 00:12:57.340
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

223
00:12:57.900 --> 00:12:59.900
What's with the getup?

224
00:12:59.900 --> 00:13:02.570
You see, today's torture...

225
00:13:04.100 --> 00:13:06.120
is xiaolongbao.

226
00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:06.920
Wha—?!

227
00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:08.210
Chinese food!

228
00:13:08.210 --> 00:13:09.280
<i>This is bad.</i>

229
00:13:09.280 --> 00:13:12.690
<i>Truth be told, Her Highness 
loves Chinese cuisine!</i>

230
00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:17.320
<i>It might be hard for her to 
overcome today's torture!</i>

231
00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:19.900
<i>Not that she ever overcomes them!</i>

232
00:13:21.260 --> 00:13:22.050
Huh?

233
00:13:22.860 --> 00:13:24.870
Is something the matter, Your Highness?

234
00:13:24.870 --> 00:13:26.680
What happened to your usual dumb face?

235
00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:27.940
Looks good...

236
00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:28.810
Dumb face?!

237
00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:33.320
It's true that I love Chinese food.

238
00:13:33.410 --> 00:13:35.500
Baminyan

239
00:13:34.410 --> 00:13:38.490
Jimochi would secretly take me to Baminyan,

240
00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:42.090
Baminyan

241
00:13:38.490 --> 00:13:40.650
the Chinese restaurant, after my lessons.

242
00:13:40.650 --> 00:13:42.080
Not again, you old fart!

243
00:13:42.330 --> 00:13:45.370
Mapo, gyoza, fried rice...

244
00:13:45.370 --> 00:13:47.100
I can't pick just one!

245
00:13:47.100 --> 00:13:52.090
Then let's order everything 
and put it all on one plate!

246
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:55.350
Yeah!

247
00:13:59.030 --> 00:14:01.760
But even for a Chinese 
cuisine die hard like me...

248
00:14:03.210 --> 00:14:05.000
Xiaolongbao are another story!

249
00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:07.370
After all, xiaolongbao 
are filled with soup,

250
00:14:07.370 --> 00:14:09.810
and always burn the inside of my mouth!

251
00:14:10.290 --> 00:14:12.110
What a pathetic reason.

252
00:14:12.370 --> 00:14:15.540
But if that's the case, we 
stand a chance of prevailing!

253
00:14:15.540 --> 00:14:16.350
Yeah.

254
00:14:16.350 --> 00:14:17.430
Princess.

255
00:14:17.950 --> 00:14:22.090
That's because you don't know the 
proper way to eat xiaolongbao.

256
00:14:22.350 --> 00:14:25.030
The proper way to eat them?

257
00:14:25.530 --> 00:14:28.900
Instead of simply putting 
one whole into your mouth,

258
00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:30.960
you begin by placing it 
atop your soup spoon,

259
00:14:31.300 --> 00:14:33.630
and then break open the skin.

260
00:14:33.640 --> 00:14:36.140
Dumb Face-o-Meter

261
00:14:35.140 --> 00:14:36.150
Your Highness!

262
00:14:36.450 --> 00:14:37.790
Keep your composure!

263
00:14:37.790 --> 00:14:40.340
